OL,3,CCan sleeper trains transform travel in
OL,4,CEurope?
OL,6,FAt the turn of the century, the growth
OL,7,Fofled to two decades of decline for
OL,8,Fsleeper trains. Orders for new
OL,9,Fcarriages disappeared, bookings
OL,10,Fdropped off and subsidies were cut.
OL,12,FBut night trains are creaking back
OL,13,Finto life.
OL,15,FDemand from passengers is growing. At
OL,16,Fleast six across Europe this year.
