OL,3,CCan sleeper trains transform travel in
OL,4,CEurope?
OL,6,FI'm on board one of them: the new
OL,7,FBrussels to Prague sleeper train. The
OL,8,Fjourney takes in four countries, four
OL,9,Fcapital cities and lasts just over 15
OL,10,Fhours.
OL,12,FITV News' Harry Horton took a tour
OL,13,Faround the compact but convenient
OL,14,Fcabins
OL,16,FWhat's interesting about this train is
OL,17,Fthat it's run by a private company,
OL,18,Fwith private investors, aiming to turn
OL,19,Fa profit.
