OL,3,CCan sleeper trains transform travel in
OL,4,CEurope?
OL,6,FFinding the right rolling stock is
OL,7,Fanother challenge.
OL,9,F"There's a huge lack of proper night
OL,10,Ftrain coaches at the moment in
OL,11,FEurope," says Chris Engelsman, one of
OL,12,Fthe co-founders of the European
OL,13,FSleeper, the company behind this new
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,16,F"There's nothing around, I mean the
OL,17,Frailways haven't been investing in
OL,18,Fnight trains for decades."
