OL,3,CCan sleeper trains transform travel in
OL,4,CEurope?
OL,6,FLots of people are embracing sleeper
OL,7,Ftrains as a more environmentally
OL,8,Ffriendly means of travelling
OL,10,FCapacity challenges have constrained
OL,11,Fthe return of night trains. Andre
OL,12,FAschwanden from the Swiss Tourism
OL,13,FOffice says it's still a small market:
OL,15,F"It's a niche. There is one train per
OL,16,Fnight, and a lot of tourists are still
OL,17,Fflying in."
