OL,3,CCan sleeper trains transform travel in
OL,4,CEurope?
OL,6,FThere is definitely a demand for new
OL,7,Fsleeper services in Europe - driven,
OL,8,Fin part, by a desire for greener
OL,9,Ftravel.
OL,11,FBut with issues around capacity and
OL,12,Favailability, a travel revolution in
OL,13,FEurope doesn't seem imminent.
